Label: Discount percentage
Description: A discount percentage applicable to the price carried in an occurrence of the <Price> composite. Optional and non-repeating; but either <DiscountPercent> or <DiscountAmount> or both must be present in each occurrence of the <Discount> composite.
Format: <dd>Real number between zero and 100 (inclusive), including explicit decimal point when required, suggested maximum length 6 characters</dd>
